Class Atom<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.Atom<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AtomDictionary, AtomInteger, AtomList, AtomString

    public abstract class Atom<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    The smallest abstract class that is extended by all other types Bencoded atom Object. The object uses Generics to allow a type or method to operate on objects of various types while providing compile-time type safety.
    Author:
    Graham Fairweather
    See Also:
    https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Generics_in_Java}
